---
import SocialPill from "./SocialPill.astro"
---

<div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        About Me
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
                Hello! I'm <span class="text-yellow-200/90 font-semibold">Jhon Henao</span>, a passionate 
                <span class="text-yellow-200/90 font-semibold">Frontend Developer</span> from the beautiful city of 
                <span class="text-yellow-200/90 font-semibold">
                    Cali, Colombia
                </span>
                . At 29 years old, I bring a wealth 
                of experience and creativity to every project I work on.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
                I specialize in creating <span class="text-yellow-200/90 font-semibold">intuitive user interfaces</span> 
                and <span class="text-yellow-200/90 font-semibold">responsive web experiences</span> that not only look 
                great but also provide exceptional functionality. My passion lies in transforming ideas into 
                interactive digital solutions that make a real impact.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
                When I'm not programming, I love exploring new technologies, exercising, and traveling to new places. I believe that continuous learning and staying up to date with the latest trends in web development 
                are essential to delivering top-notch solutions.
                That other aspect of my life (traveling) can be seen in more detail by clicking the button below.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
        <SocialPill href="/trips">
            <svg class="size-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            View my trips
        </SocialPill>
    </div>
</div>